# =================================================================
#  Configuration Example / 配置文件范例
# =================================================================
#
#  Instructions / 使用说明:
#  1. Copy this file and rename it to ".env"
#     复制此文件并重命名为 ".env"
#
#  2. Update the path below to your local Obsidian vault
#     将下方的路径修改为你本地 Obsidian 仓库的实际路径
#
# =================================================================

# [Optional] Absolute path to your Obsidian plugin folder for auto-deployment
# [可选] 你的 Obsidian 插件目录的绝对路径，用于开发时自动部署复制文件
#
# Example / 示例:
# Windows: D:\Vaults\MyVault\.obsidian\plugins\marginalia
# Mac/Linux: /Users/username/Documents/ObsidianVault/.obsidian/plugins/marginalia

OBSIDIAN_VAULT_PATH=/path/to/your/obsidian/vault/.obsidian/plugins/marginalia